node.text: FPC attorney Bill Sack breaks down Pennsylvania’s newest attacks on your rights! HR 393 would require background checks to purchase ammunition and would only allow licensed FFLs to sell it. HR 1786 would require retail ammunition manufacturers that provide their products for sale to encode their ammunition with serial numbers. Help FIGHT back against these attacks on your rights by sending a message to your reps with FPC’s “Take Action” tool at FPCAction.org!

node.title: New Pennsylvania Bills Would Attack Your Rights
